## API Reference

### Health Check
```
GET /health
→ {"status": "ok", "functions": [...]}
```

### List Functions
```
GET /functions
→ {"functionName": {"params": 2, "isVariant": false}, ...}
```

### Call Function
```
POST /call
{"fn": "functionName", "args": [arg1, arg2, ...]}
→ {"ok": true, "result": ...}
```

### Batch Call
```
POST /batch
{"calls": [{"fn": "func1", "args": [...]}, {"fn": "func2", "args": [...]}]}
→ {"ok": true, "results": [{"ok": true, "result": ...}, ...]}
```

